<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">Yes I would say it is since there is nothing vulgar or inappropriate. It is a very wholesome book and I would recommend it to anyone who loves a clean<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">Yes I would say it is since there is nothing vulgar or inappropriate. It is a very wholesome book and I would recommend it to anyone who loves a clean romance with a fairy tale twist. <a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
